{"tid":1577462,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人可唔可以應承我一樣野","createTime":"2019-09-17T16:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T02:01:18.000Z","uid":195950,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5274211e63e3623527298fb9410c0e23f55dd4d9","tid":1577462,"uid":195950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:56:00.000Z","msg":"雖然我呢三個月都有出去發夢<br />\n但係我冇開過一個關於呢場運動嘅post<br />\n今日開呢個post<br />\n係因為近日嘅活動裏面<br />\n愈來愈多私了又或者自衛等嘅情況<br />\n我好怕有一樣野嘅出現<br />\n就係去打一啲手無寸鐵<br />\n淨係言語攻擊我地嘅藍絲癈老<br />\n<br />\n你地唔好誤會我係左膠<br />\n我非常支持你地自衛<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係麻煩大家對準一啲攞武器<br />\n又或者郁手郁腳嘅人<br />\n</span></span><br />\n自衛嘅基本條件係對方威脅到你<br />\n用拳腳攻擊你，你去還手先叫做自衛<br />\n我希望大家唔好俾一時衝動<br />\n嘅嬲嘅憤怒去掩蓋自己嘅理智<br />\n我要講嘅就係咁多喇<br />\n小弟嘅表達能力唔係咁好<br />\n可能表達得唔清淅<br />\n麻煩各位見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"b75db207ee5481977ba70afd6df2cc813af8edcf","tid":1577462,"uid":195950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:56:21.000Z","msg":"自攞10次"},{"pid":"34e5403fe76eb2496210c483b0c761bcf98b872a","tid":1577462,"uid":195950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:56:33.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"80b86dad181c6692c719818aafc98ac060164778","tid":1577462,"uid":195950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:56:44.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"dff0cfa335a16003c5c138d9011b0840bdbf82f0","tid":1577462,"uid":195950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:56:54.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"3e447545750d48d98f4e091386a4637813e05272","tid":1577462,"uid":195950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:57:04.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"a694d1d752ca54d5991dad06d71f7453b517f0b2","tid":1577462,"uid":195950,"like":0,"